Package: tipitaka
Type: Package
Title: Data and Tools for Analyzing the Pali Canon
Version: 1.0.0
Authors@R:
    person(given = "Dan",
           family = "Zigmond",
           role = c("aut", "cre"),
           email = "djz@shmonk.com")
Description: Provides access to the complete Pali Canon, or
    Tipitaka, the canonical scripture for Theravadin Buddhists
    worldwide. Includes both the Chattha Sangayana Tipitaka
    (Vipassana Research Institute, 1990) and a critical edition
    of the Sutta Pitaka based on a five-witness collation
    (PTS, SuttaCentral, VRI, BJT, Thai) with lemmatization
    via the Digital Pali Dictionary and sutta-level granularity.
License: CC0
Encoding: UTF-8
